“rights”  means  all  rights,  powers,  privileges  and  immunities,
whether  present  or  future,  actual,  contingent  or  prospective,  and
whether  enforceable  in  Malaysia  or  elsewhere;

“conversion  date”  means  the  date  on  which  the  Exchange  is
converted to a public company limited by shares as appointed by
the  Minister  under  subsection  3(3);

(c) a copy of the memorandum and articles of association of
the Exchange duly amended to reflect that it is a public
company  limited  by  shares;

(a) the  amended  memorandum  and  articles  referred  to  in
paragraph 3(2)(c) shall be the memorandum and articles
of  association  of  the  Exchange;
